# Prompt AI Rules

## MUST
- Follow `docs/rules/prompt-rules.md`.
- Store prompt content in the database.
- Keep prompt metadata in `packages/prompts`.
- Use active prompt versions.
- Validate all AI output with JSON Schema.
- Log every LLM call in `llm_call_logs`.
- Include sources for market conclusions.
- Distinguish facts, inference, and sentiment.
- Say when sources are insufficient.

## RAG
- Keyword search top 10.
- Vector search top 10.
- Merge and dedupe.
- Use at most 12 context items.
- Preserve source URL and published time.

## FORBIDDEN
- No buy, sell, long, short, or leverage advice.
- No promised returns.
- No invented sources.
- No speculation presented as fact.
- No hardcoded prompt body in business code.
- No publishing AI output that failed schema validation.
